UA_Boolean UA_DataTypeMember::namespaceZero ( 1  )

The type of the member is defined in namespace zero. In this implementation, types from custom namespace may contain members from the same namespace or ns0 only.

UA_Byte UA_DataTypeMember::padding ( 5  )

How much padding is there before this member element? For arrays this is split into 2 bytes padding before the length index (max 4 bytes) and 3 bytes padding before the pointer (max 8 bytes)
